{
  "stem": "27285.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he used to have a voice, but he lost it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No, you see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can still hear if you want to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "OK, that's so much for my poor parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember, but I guess I did, because there were some-- it was possible.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] It was impossible from Terezin to write, but I don't know whether anybody ever received it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was also impossible to get packages, care packages, to Terezin, which we never saw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my parents, who didn't have anything, I mean, they came without anything to this country, to Israel-- then Palestine-- and they used to send parcels.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I never saw a parcel in the camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning of '42.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I only remember-- that is one of the strongest memories of mine, is this, being crowded all the time, being crowded.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never having the possibility to be by yourself a little bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was always very shy, and tried to read a book, or something, but it was impossible, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember-- this goes back, again, to the orphanage-- summertime we were sent always-- always-- I mean three, four, years we were there-- to Czech villages, to Jewish families who were in a better position, materially, and they took in orphans.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So whenever they were looking for me, I was in-- also I was scared sick to-- of any cow, or anything bigger than a little dog.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were there, somehow, I was in the stable, with a book, finally being a little bit by myself.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I needed this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was [INAUDIBLE], but it was-- so that my memory of camps is only very, very crowded, of course no privacy at all.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
